The Kenya Civil Aviation Authority is set to host for the first time the Civil Air Navigation Services Organization (CANSO) conference 2018 in Mombasa on the 3rd to 7th of September. Canso is a global voice of air traffic management seeking to improve air navigation services internationally. Aviation experts from air traffic management, air navigation providers air traffic management system manufacturers and airline operators globally will be gathered together to interact and improve the air traffic management. This will be a positive forum to help improve the traffic flow.